The \mbox{\hyperlink{class_open_x_l_s_x_1_1_x_l_xml_file}{XLXml\+File}} class provides an interface for derived classes to use. It functions as an ancestor to all classes which are represented by an .xml file in an .xlsx package.

\doxysubsection{Detailed Description}
The \mbox{\hyperlink{class_open_x_l_s_x_1_1_x_l_xml_file}{XLXml\+File}} class provides an interface for derived classes to use. It functions as an ancestor to all classes which are represented by an .xml file in an .xlsx package. 

\begin{DoxyWarning}{Warning}
The \mbox{\hyperlink{class_open_x_l_s_x_1_1_x_l_xml_file}{XLXml\+File}} class is not intended to be instantiated on it\textquotesingle{}s own, but to provide an interface for derived classes. Also, it should not be used polymorphically. For that reason, the destructor is not declared virtual. 
\end{DoxyWarning}
